metadata.name: Brooklyn 9.30.2011
metadata.description:
Winner of the auction please email kithfriends@invisiblefriends.io to verify and claim your Kith product.

In celebration of our partnership between Kith and Invisible Friends. This Friend references Kith's first store opening in Brooklyn, NY which opened on September 30, 2011. The Friend is seen wearing a key look from Kith's Men's Summer 2022 Collection as well as an upcoming sneaker partnership. 

Winner of this auction will recieve a Serif K Cap, Napeague Sunglasses, SS Linden Retro Quarter Zip, Turbo Shorts, Script Socks, and a special ftw collaboration.
